    <div data-cid="6704057">
        <div class="main review-item" id="6704057">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4709512/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/icon/u4709512-4.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4709512/" class="name">旸谷</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2014-06-16" class="main-meta">2014-06-16 20:32:39</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/20397330/">河南文艺出版社2013版</a>
            </span>
    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6704057/">最美其实林诗音，终老要选孙小红</a></h2>

                <div id="review_6704057_short" class="review-short" data-rid="6704057">
                    <div class="short-content">

                               林仙儿的戏份真是太多了。让人感觉整部书好像是由她串联起来的。从梅花盗到上官金虹，从郭嵩阳到荆无命，再到吕奉先。游龙生、伊哭、龙小云这些人也与其有染。                她的美也着墨颇多。没有男人舍得下手杀她，吕奉先还因为她杀了玲玲；阿飞险些为她与李寻欢断...

